{"tid":1525026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]有咩方法可以用國際人道法去清算班仆街黑警？","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T02:51:19.000Z","uid":158497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a13ff9b808a8097aa766dd791a9740f18ff3b2a","tid":1525026,"uid":158497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:13:44.000Z","msg":"黑警阻礙救護: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1523777/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1523777/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n跟據國際人道法:<br />\n<br />\n由於在戰場上醫療人員使用了明顯的紅十字標記，他們可以不受阻礙地向受難者提供救助。<br />\n<br />\n在武裝衝突時期，保護國（即由敵對行動各方所挑選的中立國）和 紅十字國際委員會 都會監督和觀察國際人道法的條文是否被遵守。<br />\n <br />\n2002年7月1日成立於海牙的 國際刑事法院是由國際法在聯合國系統以外建立的永久性機構。如果國家司法機關沒有能力或不願意審理犯有種族滅絕罪、戰爭罪和危害人類罪的人，國際刑事法院將補充這一國內司法之不足。<br />\nsource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icrc.org/zh/doc/assets/files/other/icrc_006_1090.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icrc.org%2Fzh%2Fdoc%2Fassets%2Ffiles%2Fother%2Ficrc_006_1090.pdf&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=8d438008\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icrc.org/zh/doc/assets/files/other/icrc_006_1090.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/rcmovement/ihl.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redcross.org.hk%2Ftc%2Frcmovement%2Fihl.html&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=469828c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/rcmovement/ihl.html</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲入黎幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37321f8e54e1193378c813ef6bdbe3061026f201","tid":1525026,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:13:55.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SI